    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://dnozza.github.io/authors/debora/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://dnozza.github.io/authors/debora/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a Postdoctoral Research Fellow in Computer Science at the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bidsa.unibocconi.eu/&#34;&gt;Bocconi Institute for Data Science and Analytics at Bocconi University&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://milanlproc.github.io/&#34;&gt;Bocconi NLP group&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.bidsa.unibocconi.eu/wps/wcm/connect/Site/Bidsa/Home/News_Events/ERC+Dirk+Hovy&#34;&gt;INTEGRATOR&lt;/a&gt; ERC Starting Grant project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My research interests mainly focus on the detection and counter-acting of &lt;a href=&#34;publication/2021-zeroshot-crosslingual-hate-speech&#34;&gt;hate speech&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;publication/2019_unintended_bias_misogyny_detection&#34;&gt;bias&lt;/a&gt; which has become fundamental for fighting against several types of discrimination that subsist in Social Media. I organized several shared tasks for the problem of hate speech, and in particular misogyny detection (&lt;a href=&#34;http://alt.qcri.org/semeval2019/&#34;&gt;HatEval@SemEval 2019&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://amievalita2020.github.io/&#34;&gt;AMI@Evalita 2020&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.evalita.it/2018&#34;&gt; AMI@Evalita 2018&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
